The article provides information on how to watch President Biden's State of the Union speech live. The speech will be delivered on Tuesday, February 7, 2023, at 9 PM ET. To watch it, you can visit WH.gov/sotu or tune into the official social media streams of the White House, including YouTube, Twitter, and Facebook. The White House feed will also include ASL interpretation for accessibility. Additionally, if you're interested, you can visit WH.gov/sotu-2022 to view last year's speech or read excerpts from this year's address.